       wisdom:"You maintain everyone else's wellbeing and treat your own as optional. But your energy is the engine everything else runs on. Building it isn't indulgence — <strong>it's the most practical investment you can make. A stronger you makes everything else possible.</strong>"},
      {type:'release',label:'RELEASE · FREE YOUR STRENGTH',title:"Put down what drains you",
       body:"For each, decide: protect it, build it, or release the guilt that's been stopping you from claiming it."},
      {type:'reclaim',label:'RECLAIM · FILL THE SPACE',title:"What will you grow toward?",
       body:"Making room is only half of it. The space you just cleared is for something. This is where capacity turns into aliveness.",
