      {type:'wisdom',label:'THE ORDER OF CARE, HERE',
       wisdom:"The deepest inversion: you've poured into everyone and given yourself almost nothing — and called it being responsible. But the self you keep putting last is the source everyone draws on. <strong>Investing in her isn't taking from anyone. It's how you become someone with more to give, and more to live for.</strong>"},
